Package: gitview-bridge
Version: @VERSION@
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: git
Recommends: nodejs (>= 20)
Maintainer: Aldwin Akbar <aldwinakbar@gmail.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/teapotlaboratories/git-view
Description: GitView bridge - git + Claude bridge for the GitView Android app
 Serves a git repository (read and working-tree write) over REST and a
 WebSocket, and drives or attaches Claude Agent sessions, for the GitView
 Android client. Runs as a systemd service (gitview-bridge.service).
 .
 Requires Node.js >= 20 at runtime. If node is not on the system PATH, set
 GITVIEW_NODE in /etc/default/gitview-bridge. Front it with Tailscale Serve -
 never expose a read/write bridge on a public network.
